title: Crazy Leveling System
description: Crazy Leveling System As a game fan, the protagonist travels to a peculiar fantasy world, where there are all kinds of gangs and sects, there are all kinds of fantasy martial arts and magic weapons, there are foreign warcraft and the strongest dragons, spirit monsters and ghosts, but No matter what sect, what big family young master, what empire prince, no matter how enchanting talent, no matter how powerful cultivation base, in the face of the main character’s crazy leveling system, they will be left far behind! Crazy Upgrade System Fēngkuáng Shēngjí Xìtǒng 疯狂升级系统
